    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so the paint is flawless and the interior is still crisp and clean. It drives like an absolute dream and has been my total pride and joy. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
