      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-division engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, with the high-pressure double-VANOS system recently calibrated for optimal valve timing. Power is routed through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential, ensuring maximum longitudinal and lateral traction. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension geometry is preserved with fresh bushings and dampers, maintaining the car's celebrated turn-in response and damping rates. Free of any fluid seepage or oxidation, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history available. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 44500.0,
