    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen, preserved in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one, reflected in its flawless, deep-gloss exterior finish and an interior that still retains that new-car scent. Every panel is original, with zero imperfections, scratches, or dents. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine runs with surgical precision, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history documenting every scheduled maintenance performed by certified technicians. The leather remains supple without a single crease, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule piece for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
