    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in a state of meticulous preservation. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity, free from wear or compromise. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that meets the most exacting standards. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in showroom condition, suited for the most demanding collector or enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical and aesthetic excellence.",
