      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. Everything is super clean, shiny, and works perfectly. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make the next owner incredibly happy! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
