    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a definitive example of JDM engineering, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. The sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, paired with the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the drivetrain remains unmodified, retaining the original Torsen limited-slip differential and stock double-wishbone suspension geometry. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. Every bushing, vacuum line, and synchro performs with the tactile precision of a showroom-fresh vehicle. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and total OEM fidelity.",
